Little Neck Parkway, east side, opposite Eightieth Ave., showing, E. Hultzz house in 1891, and the M. Wesnofski house and farm from 1896-1909. This house does not appear in the 1928 Atlas.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
